Cell["\<\
        List(List(Rule(Derivative(0,1)(delU)(t,x),
     -    (-2*x**2*dudtau(i)*ia2B(i)**2 + 
     -       2*x*dudtauB(i)*f(i)*ia2B(i)**2 - 
